MatchedRegions.transcript: We evaluated the performance of four kinds of models, statistic, machine learning models, neural networks, general-domain large-scale pre-trained language models, and COVID-19-related pre-trained language models for the NER task and the TSA task on MassCov dataset.

MatchedRegion.Text: We reported the results based on experiments on 5 different random seeds: 22, 32, 42, 52 and 62.
